metadata.name: Kangaroo Punch Club #1
metadata.description: Made by VFX artist Eddy Tavus, who has worked for Universal, Arcane and many others. Kangaroo punch club is an NFT collection of unique 3D characters built with a sophisticated variety of distinctive traits on the Etherum Blockchain. Each NFT is packed with utility. Serving as more than a cool PFP, a Kangaroo Punch Club NFT will serve as an exclusive playable fighter in our ever-expanding Metaverse Game Kangaroo Punch Arena
